Bon Voyage!




To this Krug drew the attention of the driver; who, without turning his head, remarked that there were many inexplicable things happening nowadays (a euphemism for 'new regime') and that it was better not to study current phenomena too closely. David tugged at his father's sleeve and wanted to know what it was all ab